data.description: Step into modern luxury with this beautifully updated 3200 sq ft, five bedroom, three bathroom home in Walton Heights. The amazing kitchen boasts a spacious island, a pot filler above the stove, and a double oven. Retreat to the master where you'll find a magazine-worthy closet offering ample space for your wardrobe. Enjoy the comfort and feel of new carpeting throughout the basement. This home blends elegance with functional living space. Come see for yourself. It will not be on the market long!
